---
title: Crispy Polenta Cakes with Sautéed Spinach & Goat Cheese
description: Mushrooms and garlic are a match made in heaven. Layer roasted zucchini, tangy tomato sauce, and crispy polenta, then serve over garlicky sautéed spinach to round out this colorful Italian feast.
